snippet.textDisplay:
The past & the future both are always happening in our present. The past with its reality of having existed (beyond our memory) & constantly shaping our thoughts, things we avoid or do and associations...
The future with our words, actions and thoughts. As humans, we only have control over shaping the future to quiet an extent in our present. But what if we could alter the past to change the future in our present? I feel thats what this film will be about
